763d1a27-bc5f-4bc9-8179-b23d743ce9e4.text: The Riviera Dining Set in Teak Natural, includes an 80''L x 40''W x 30''H table and eight armchairs, each measuring 24''W x 26''D x 35''H. fa327d91-fffa-4da9-a0d1-1e593206f3b9.text: The Sawyer Patio Umbrella in Ecru Sand, measuring 120'' in diameter with a 102'' height, offers a square, vented canopy with a bamboo pole and ribs. The rotational tilt and crank lift mechanisms allow for easy adjustment. Manufactured by SawyerShade.
